  "detailed_description": "Custom Machinery is a block based building game in which you can build vehicles and other machines, configure their parts and use them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709820/extras/b351920dc43892337563afbe78d16fe6.poster.avif?t=1631560914\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709820/extras/b351920dc43892337563afbe78d16fe6.webm?t=1631560914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709820/extras/b351920dc43892337563afbe78d16fe6.mp4?t=1631560914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Currently there are 42 different blocks many of which are highly configurable.Of these blocks there are 3 seperate types;<br>-Structural Blocks: Blocks that are used for giving the vehicle its shape.<br>-Movement Blocks: Blocks that move the vehicle by applying force to it.<br>-Shape Changer Blocks: Blocks that change the shape of the vehicle.<br><br>Vehicles can be saved in a text file and can be loaded from one. Which means they can be shared anywhere on the internet.",
  "about_the_game": "Custom Machinery is a block based building game in which you can build vehicles and other machines, configure their parts and use them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709820/extras/b351920dc43892337563afbe78d16fe6.poster.avif?t=1631560914\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709820/extras/b351920dc43892337563afbe78d16fe6.webm?t=1631560914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709820/extras/b351920dc43892337563afbe78d16fe6.mp4?t=1631560914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Currently there are 42 different blocks many of which are highly configurable.Of these blocks there are 3 seperate types;<br>-Structural Blocks: Blocks that are used for giving the vehicle its shape.<br>-Movement Blocks: Blocks that move the vehicle by applying force to it.<br>-Shape Changer Blocks: Blocks that change the shape of the vehicle.<br><br>Vehicles can be saved in a text file and can be loaded from one. Which means they can be shared anywhere on the internet.",
